WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:01.377
Good morning, family.

00:00:01.377 --> 00:00:03.159
How have you all been doing?

00:00:03.346 --> 00:00:07.933
I hope you're doing well.

00:00:07.933 --> 00:00:11.360
I have some things on my heart to tell you.

00:00:11.360 --> 00:00:35.879
First, I'm going to tell you what the Lord is talking to me about: a diet.

00:00:47.693 --> 00:01:07.940
A lot of people are asking how I'm losing weight, and it's just what the Holy Spirit has been talking to me about.

00:01:09.185 --> 00:01:45.550
He said to me that for the days that are coming—he even brought it up in my dreams last night—there is a plague coming.

00:01:45.550 --> 00:01:59.866
He said, 'Brandon, there is a plague, another massive wave.

00:01:59.866 --> 00:03:04.013
' The first wave was COVID from 2020 until 2022, and it receded, but he said there will be a day soon when there will be another plague, and this one will dwarf COVID.

00:03:06.900 --> 00:03:17.359
A lot of people will perish because of this.

00:03:18.760 --> 00:03:54.874
He said, 'I want you to tell my people that it's time for them to take their health more seriously.

00:03:54.874 --> 00:04:07.900
' They need to start exercising, even just walking.

00:04:07.900 --> 00:04:29.170
Exercise is important for getting your blood flowing and taking care of your bodies.

00:04:29.170 --> 00:04:40.020
It needs to become a lifestyle habit.

00:04:40.020 --> 00:05:06.267
The Lord said it doesn't have to be a long time, just 30 minutes a day or every other day, but start keeping your body moving.

00:05:06.267 --> 00:05:44.228
I asked the Lord for a lifestyle to maintain weight, and he instructed me to go on a Whole Foods diet: beef, chicken, fish, vegetables, fruit, and eggs.

00:05:44.228 --> 00:06:17.657
He said if you read a label at the market and can't pronounce half the ingredients, do not put it in your body.

00:06:17.657 --> 00:06:23.547
He said, 'Brandon, they are poisoning you, and you don't even know it.

00:06:23.547 --> 00:06:36.634
' My people perish for a lack of knowledge.

00:06:36.634 --> 00:07:08.600
If you are not studying and don't know what's on that label, do not consume it.

00:07:08.600 --> 00:07:32.879
Eat things that do not have a nutrition label; fish is fish, and chicken is chicken.

00:07:32.879 --> 00:07:38.608
Stay with Whole Foods.

00:07:38.608 --> 00:08:25.873
Then he talked to me about supplements and how many companies are not good; they are in it for profit and use unhealthy ingredients.

00:08:25.873 --> 00:08:42.951
My wife is very educated and is looking up trustworthy companies.

00:08:44.360 --> 00:09:22.702
I used to take all kinds of vitamins, but the Lord told me to stop because I didn't know what they were putting in them.

00:09:22.702 --> 00:09:26.232
Study the brand of vitamin you are taking and who is making it.

00:09:26.232 --> 00:09:55.451
There are many different opinions, so you have to follow the Holy Spirit for your own life.

00:09:55.451 --> 00:10:18.630
I believe if you keep it under 1,500 calories and exercise, you'll drop weight.

00:10:18.630 --> 00:10:39.676
I'm learning that my body doesn't need as much as it used to.

00:10:39.676 --> 00:11:13.451
You don't have to snack all the time; you can intermittent fast and take care of your body.

00:11:14.582 --> 00:11:31.453
It doesn't have to be an addiction to food.

00:11:32.049 --> 00:12:04.350
I was codependent on junk, but I am determined to live long and finish strong.

00:12:04.350 --> 00:12:15.959
Secondly, the Lord spoke to me about the youth.

00:12:15.959 --> 00:12:34.396
They are looking for an authentic move of the Spirit.

00:12:34.396 --> 00:12:46.519
They are hungry for the supernatural.

00:13:01.472 --> 00:13:21.040
He said there's been a lot of charismatic flakiness and fleshly behavior in churches, which is a turn-off for them.

00:13:21.040 --> 00:13:43.519
What's coming next will be a weight of the tangible presence of my Shekinah Glory.

00:13:45.552 --> 00:14:26.542
The presence of the Lord will come into the atmosphere of the church to the point where it affects the whole congregation.

00:14:32.960 --> 00:14:45.879
There will be no mistaking it or mocking it.

00:14:45.879 --> 00:15:31.374
You will feel the weight of the tangible presence of God so strongly that there will be a holy hush upon the congregation.

00:15:46.248 --> 00:16:03.886
You won't want to move because the fear of the Lord is tangible in that building.

00:16:03.886 --> 00:16:46.800
There is a holy reverence where you just want to sit and weep before the presence and the power of the Lord.

00:16:49.954 --> 00:17:35.787
The Lord told me there will be a move of his Spirit in churches that feels like a weight on the people, including the children.

00:17:35.787 --> 00:17:46.046
I'm so excited this is coming.

00:17:46.046 --> 00:18:15.704
He said, 'I will have the harvest of souls from this generation like this world has never seen before.

00:18:15.704 --> 00:18:41.577
' They are searching for a move of something to help their depression and anxiety.

00:18:41.577 --> 00:18:49.954
He also talked about Europe.

00:18:49.954 --> 00:19:08.382
Over a year ago, I saw soldiers in a single file line going toward Europe.

00:19:08.382 --> 00:19:21.159
It was a major draft.

00:19:25.691 --> 00:19:55.120
The Lord showed me that the war had escalated into a World War III scenario.

00:20:14.720 --> 00:20:19.866
I heard that the great Apollyon is being released upon the Earth.

00:20:29.280 --> 00:20:41.360
I saw a massive, demonic-looking angelic being—a huge principality—come out of the ocean.

00:20:51.200 --> 00:21:16.559
I saw a demon chained in a pit, and an angelic being from the Lord came down and released that spirit.

00:21:44.509 --> 00:21:55.354
It looked like it was wearing a fur Viking outfit with thick white hair and a horned helmet.

00:21:55.354 --> 00:21:59.720
Its face was vicious.

00:22:01.790 --> 00:22:31.228
It started spinning like the Tasmanian Devil and went inside Vladimir Putin, as if he became possessed.

00:22:39.911 --> 00:22:49.576
All of a sudden, I saw him strike Poland because Poland was provoking Russia.

00:22:49.576 --> 00:23:06.354
Near the Warsaw and Belarus area, I saw a humongous mushroom cloud explosion.

00:23:06.354 --> 00:23:39.259
I thought they were tactical nukes, but the Lord said, 'No, this is a weapon that has never been used before.

00:23:39.259 --> 00:23:50.640
' It vaporized everything in a huge radius.

00:23:50.640 --> 00:24:06.138
When this happened, World War III escalated even more.

00:24:06.138 --> 00:24:21.395
Turkey joined in with Russia, funding them and beating ancient drums.

00:24:21.395 --> 00:24:37.059
Then Iran joined them, and they came against Israel.

00:24:44.893 --> 00:24:52.600
I saw men with red hats marching toward Israel.

00:24:53.400 --> 00:25:10.210
The Lord told me this is the beginning of the Ezekiel 38 and 39 war—Gog and Magog.

00:25:10.210 --> 00:25:21.933
The United States did not participate because we were busy with Europe.

00:25:37.908 --> 00:25:41.773
People called it 'the Great Betrayal' because we did not help Israel.

00:25:50.520 --> 00:25:58.139
I saw China shoot something that looked like a red dragon over America.

00:25:58.139 --> 00:26:14.667
I saw a surprise attack on Hawaii, similar to Pearl Harbor.

00:26:14.667 --> 00:26:38.426
Honolulu and the Big Island were at war with China, and they were bombing the people with F-16s.

00:26:38.426 --> 00:26:55.094
Fast forward to today: none of this was happening two years ago.

00:27:05.647 --> 00:27:28.600
Now we hear about the Prime Minister of France talking about nuclear weapons within NATO, and Putin saying this would be the beginning of World War III.

00:27:28.600 --> 00:27:39.032
We are seeing the escalation against Iran.

00:27:47.840 --> 00:28:08.919
In 2022, an angel told me in a dream that great judgment would begin 569 days from that day.

00:28:16.159 --> 00:28:27.771
That math pointed to October 2nd, and then Israel was attacked on October 7th, 2023.

00:28:27.771 --> 00:28:51.633
I warned everyone to watch August 24th, 2023, which was when Saudi Arabia joined the BRICS nations.

00:28:59.707 --> 00:29:05.640
The Lord brought up the dollar again last night.

00:29:05.640 --> 00:29:25.840
He said the purchasing power of the dollar will be around 50 cents.

00:29:25.840 --> 00:29:58.617
He said there will be a major event that causes a significant stock market crash, similar to 1930.

00:29:58.617 --> 00:30:04.908
He said it's coming.

00:30:12.725 --> 00:30:44.858
I told you all to watch the mulberry tree at wintertime and to stay on the back of your rug.

00:30:44.858 --> 00:31:03.919
It's fixing to happen in Poland—in the Warsaw and Belarus area.

00:31:03.919 --> 00:31:11.542
God protect those people.

00:31:14.180 --> 00:31:31.293
We know these things must happen because they are biblical.

00:31:31.293 --> 00:31:58.559
Regarding the plague and the 'pale' horse, it's part of the end times.

00:32:00.252 --> 00:32:30.559
The Lord is coming back for a glorious church that is on fire and victorious.

00:32:30.559 --> 00:32:49.800
There is a mighty move of God about to happen.

00:32:49.800 --> 00:33:24.080
A supernatural event is about to take place with finances where the wealth of the sinner is laid up for the just.

00:33:27.308 --> 00:33:38.813
Father, we thank you for every person represented here.

00:33:47.160 --> 00:33:58.754
We call their unsaved loved ones into the kingdom of God.

00:34:04.720 --> 00:34:27.839
We break the bondage of darkness and call them to be flooded with light.

00:34:27.839 --> 00:34:40.589
Raise up new Davids, Daniels, and Joshuas.

00:34:48.855 --> 00:35:02.635
We call for healing over every person: those with high blood sugar, diabetes, or heart disease.

00:35:10.897 --> 00:35:12.982
We call for new kidneys, hearts, and livers.

00:35:15.639 --> 00:35:19.160
We curse cancer and Alzheimer's.

00:35:24.760 --> 00:35:38.570
We call for healing over stomach viruses and thyroid issues.

00:35:38.940 --> 00:35:50.417
We bless every person who supports this channel.

00:35:50.417 --> 00:35:55.651
We are going from glory to glory in the name of Jesus.

00:35:55.651 --> 00:35:57.708
Amen.
